essential beach boys if you 're looking for a collection of just the hits , stick with 2003 's sounds of summer . if you need a nostalgia fix for the beach boys ' best albums of the sixties through the mid-seventies , pick up the two-fers of their classic albums from surfin ' safari through surf 's up . however , if you want a solid overview of america 's most influential band and why brian wilson is regarded as a genius , wrap your ears around this 5-disc good vibrations box set . brian wilson and company take you on a magical history tour from their debut single `` surfin ' '' to their final no . 1 , `` kokomo . '' essentia